{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_VolcanoSet}}
'''A_VolcanoSet'''<br />
(no parameters)

Changes the calling state's remaining duration from its default value (normally 35 in the {{Class|Volcano}}'s Spawn+1 state) to a random value between 105 and 232.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Volcano}} and derived classes.

